within the hour.

366
00:30:07,972 --> 00:30:09,973
- Well, if you...
- (LINE CLICKS, HUMS)

367
00:30:09,974 --> 00:30:12,475
Hello?

368
00:30:15,814 --> 00:30:17,022
You again?

369
00:30:17,023 --> 00:30:20,942
