419
00:34:16,888 --> 00:34:18,513
Thank you.

420
00:34:23,728 --> 00:34:26,897
- You ready to order?
- Yes. What would you like?

421
00:34:26,898 --> 00:34:30,650
- Well, I'm a little short of cash.
- WENDY: You can owe me.

422
00:34:30,651 --> 00:34:33,987
