what kind of beer you got?

424
00:34:37,200 --> 00:34:39,117
Come on, man,
this is a drive-in, not a bar.

425
00:34:39,118 --> 00:34:40,786
All right, don't get nervous.

426
00:34:40,787 --> 00:34:42,788
