497
00:40:26,298 --> 00:40:28,966
Over there.

498
00:40:33,722 --> 00:40:35,265
HENRI-ANNE: Can you both hear me?

499
00:40:35,266 --> 00:40:36,975
Yes.

500
00:40:36,976 --> 00:40:39,477
- HENRI-ANNE: Can you hear me, Kim?
- Mm-hm.

501
00:40:39,478 --> 00:40:41,688
